  "text": "Stereotypical notions of Aboriginality are extremely problematic and countering these is of great significance to addressing discrimination of Indigenous peoples in Australia [CITATION_1] . The mentors' narratives revealed both the erroneous viewpoints that individuals can have as well as the learning and self-discovery that participants underwent as mentors in the program.",
